# Character Archetypes

Your archetype represents your professional training—the skills, techniques, and capabilities that define your role in the party. Where your calling shapes who you are psychologically, your archetype determines what you can do practically.

Every archetype provides a complete starting package: combat-ready skills, specialized capabilities, professional equipment, and a unique subsystem that sets it apart from others. Whether you want to be an armored defender, a precise archer, a master of magic, or something else entirely, your archetype gives you the foundation to excel.

